data.description: ** $6,000 Price Improvement!** Discover an exquisite find in the serene surroundings of Cantonment's Robinsons Mill Subdivision. Situated conveniently close to schools and shopping centers, this residence offers an inviting open floor plan and ample space for your family. Boasting 10-foot step-up ceilings, a generously sized covered patio, and a delightful covered lanai, this home is an oasis of comfort. The luxurious features continue with an expansive master bathroom, complete with an oversized layout. The large bonus room over the garage comes with a separate closet and full bathroom, offering versatility and additional space for your needs. Enjoy the spacious kitchen with its large island, ideal for hosting gatherings or enjoying family cookouts, while overlooking the cozy family space. Vaulted ceilings add an air of grandeur, while granite countertops adorn both the kitchen and all bathrooms, elevating the aesthetic appeal. The master bedroom includes a walk-in closet, seamlessly connected to the laundry room through a separate door, providing optimal convenience. Outside, the property boasts ample backyard space, perfect for the addition of a pool and deck, a serene wooded rest area, a charming fire pit, or even a whimsical tree house. With a sprawling 600+ square foot 2-car garage/storage space, this home effortlessly combines functionality with elegance. Embodying a captivating craftsman style, this home is a must-see. Contact us today for an exclusive tour!
